text:
Bassil has appointed himself as an agent for the President of the Republic .. & quot; & quot;
06 Nov 2019, 09:41 by Lebanon 24
Ghassan Rifi wrote in the "Ambassador of the North": There is no doubt that the vast majority of Lebanese, regardless of their orientations, sects and doctrines, appreciate the President of the Republic, General Michel Aoun, and respect his person, and recognize his struggle history and national symbolism, and many of them hastened to close their political differences with him when he became They are looking forward to the success of his reign to save Lebanon and realize the slogan of reform and change that he brought. Three years have passed since the reign of President Aoun. The Lebanese agree that nothing has been achieved in reform, and no one has seen an iota of change. Regardless of the reasons, the determination of responsibilities and the defamation of accusations in every direction, the general Lebanese situation will speak for itself and the popular revolution. Launched on the eve of the state's remedy, it was the biggest evidence of the desperation, despair and lack of prospects for any solution in an economy that is collapsing, a declining lira, a contaminated environment, rampant diseases, crises, poverty, as well as brutal corruption, waste, theft, brokering and suspicious deals. Sectarian disease Some Lebanese talked about the crisis of the regime that prevents the achievement of achievements quickly, but what they do not accept is the shaking of the image of their sworn president to defend them and protect their constitution. The Palace of Baabda and the Lord of the Covenant, which grieves in the hearts of the Lebanese, should be exposed to a symbol of its national value for all this amount of abuse. Some of the protesters of the Tishrin Revolution may have erred in hurting the country's president, but they may be accompanied by their poverty, pain and suffering, their growing sense of alienation in their homeland, and their departure from power living on another planet far from their aspirations, aspirations and demands. The mistake that is supposed to be held accountable, is the behavior of Minister Bassil, who acts as if the mayor of the Presidency of the Republic receives visitors in the corridors of the Palace of Baabda, and conducts consultations to form a government, and refuses to strike the Constitution, which is going to protect his uncle President, and deals with others with superiority, and carries on His shoulders are various accusations of suspicious deals. Bassil continues to antagonize the Lebanese sects, parties and citizens, most of whom are Christians and even Maronites, which led to the isolation of the Free Patriotic Movement in its environment, in the face of entrenched differences with the Lebanese forces and the rebel, the Phalanges, the Liberals, the National Bloc and the independents, while it does not hesitate to antagonize the Muslims, a year of During the Sunni political accusation that it came on the body of the Maronite political, and the harness of the judiciary to undermine some of their symbols, and Shiites accused President Nabih Berri bullying, and Druza to dig up graves and provocation, which led to the incident of Qabrishmon, which almost sparked a new civil war. Bassil has appointed himself as an agent of the President of the Republic in all matters, so that some accuse his "Excellency" of being "defeated" before the ambitions of the brother-in-law, who also deliberately or inadvertently distorted the image of the "President of the Republic", by introducing him as a partner and sponsor of the Baabda march. Organized by his political current and aims to polish his image and demonstrate his popular strength using the power he represents in the face of citizens demanding bread, justice and freedom. All this and many other forms of several abuses of the President of the Republic rejected by the Lebanese people, which is increasingly hostile to those who cause them, as rejected by the family of President Aoun, which faces a clear division over what Basil is doing. Perhaps what expressed by Mrs. Claudine Aoun Roukoz This behavior, and the relentless quest to protect President Aoun from irresponsible practices and actions, and from the presidential ambitions that may end Aoun's premature premature, especially as what was going on whispering within the family began to come out publicly that "enough insults to the President of the Republic symbol of the country ".
